edu.ncsu.csc216.incident_management.model.incident

Class ManagedIncident

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc216.incident_management.model.incident.ManagedIncident

  • public class ManagedIncident
extends java.lang.Object
    creates the class that allows for the creation of an incident and that also manages those incidents (updating and managing them)
    Author:
    William
